text: The Voyager series is a group of high speed diesel electric multiple unit trains built by Bombardier Transportation in service on the UK railway network. The trains are among the most modern currently in operation, and are in service on many intercity routes around Great Britain. There are currently three types in service with 3TOCs (, East Midlands railway avanti and CrossCountry). Category:British Rail diesel multiple units
title: Bombardier Voyager family
